reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Reliable and Affordable
reviews.reviewText: As an Apple enthusiast, I've always held high standards for accessories that complement my beloved devices. This 3 Pack of Apple MFi Certified Lightning Cables has truly impressed me. First off, the fact that they're MFi certified brings peace of mind, ensuring compatibility and safety for my iPhone 14 down to my older models like the SE.The length of these cables is a game-changer. At 10 feet each, they provide ample reach, allowing me to comfortably use my device while it's charging, whether I'm lounging on the couch or tucked into bed. The nylon braided design not only adds durability but also prevents tangling, which is a constant annoyance with lesser cables.What I appreciate most is the fast-charging capability. In today's fast-paced world, every minute counts, and these cables deliver efficient charging without compromising on safety. Whether I'm topping up my battery before heading out or juicing up during a work break, the speed is noticeable and appreciated.Overall, this 3 Pack of Lightning Cables is a must-have for any Apple user seeking reliability, durability, and fast charging. It's a testament to Apple's commitment to quality, and I wholeheartedly recommend it to fellow enthusiasts and everyday users alike.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lifesaver at the hospital
reviews.reviewText: I ordered these because everyone said I needed a long charger during labor and oh my goodness these saved my butt. First, I love the color options. I got to use the one that matched my baby's gender! Second, the cables themselves are sturdy. They don't look like they will rip or snap at the end like others I've had. They are also LONG, which is exactly what I needed. The outlet in both my labor and post-delivery room was nowhere near my bed and I was grateful I got these so I could keep my phone handy during the few days I was there. They kept my phone charged the entire time.
